{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"zettel.20260420061007","title":"Halaman Software Architecture Guide adalah peta keputusan, bukan tutorial implementasi","desc":"Fowler mengatur halaman ini sebagai ringkasan konsep dan peta judgment untuk arsitektur, bukan deep-dive teknis.","tags":["permanent-note","software-architecture","architecture","martin-fowler"],"custom":{},"fname":"zettel.20260420061007","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"fb3a7ed6092a83e2feaecca83792daf4","updated":1776683200312,"created":1776683200312,"links":[{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420061007","id":"zettel.20260420061007","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.permanent-note","alias":"permanent-note","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.permanent-note"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420061007","id":"zettel.20260420061007","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.software-architecture","alias":"software-architecture","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.software-architecture"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420061007","id":"zettel.20260420061007","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.architecture","alias":"architecture","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.architecture"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420061007","id":"zettel.20260420061007","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.martin-fowler","alias":"martin-fowler","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.martin-fowler"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420061007","id":"zettel.20260420061007","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.literature.software-architecture-guide","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":3,"offset":930},"end":{"line":22,"column":52,"offset":979},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.literature.software-architecture-guide"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420061007","id":"zettel.20260420061007","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.20260420060847","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":3,"offset":1030},"end":{"line":23,"column":28,"offset":1055},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260420060847"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420061007","id":"zettel.20260420061007","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.20260420060928","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":3,"offset":1113},"end":{"line":24,"column":28,"offset":1138},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260420060928"}},{"from":{"fname":"zettel","id":"zettel","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":3,"offset":2113},"end":{"line":33,"column":28,"offset":2138},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420061007"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","id":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":3,"offset":2302},"end":{"line":40,"column":28,"offset":2327},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420061007"}],"anchors":{},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"halaman-software-architecture-guide-adalah-peta-keputusan-bukan-tutorial-implementasi\">Halaman Software Architecture Guide adalah peta keputusan, bukan tutorial implementasi<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#halaman-software-architecture-guide-adalah-peta-keputusan-bukan-tutorial-implementasi\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>\"This page outlines my view of software architecture and points you to more material about architecture on this site.\"</p>\n<p>Sumber: <a href=\"https://martinfowler.com/architecture/\">https://martinfowler.com/architecture/</a></p>\n<p>Paragraf ini menunjukkan bahwa halaman ini dimaksudkan sebagai peta konsep, bukan panduan implementasi.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Catatan gue:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Halaman ini bukan tutorial implementasi atau blueprint teknis.</li>\n<li>Fowler membangun space untuk membedakan apa yang penting dalam arsitektur dan membuka cabang bacaan lanjutan.</li>\n<li>Jadi konteks baca yang tepat adalah sebagai \"index of judgment\": panduan untuk mengenali area keputusan yang paling relevan.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Implikasi:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Pembaca harus fokus pada logika dan kerangka berpikir, bukan mencari solusi siap pakai di setiap paragraf.</li>\n<li>Keputusan yang penting bisa berubah tergantung konteks tim, aplikasi, dan organisasi.</li>\n<li>Ringkasan seperti ini lebih berharga sebagai landasan diskusi daripada referensi implementasi langsung.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Hubungan:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.software-architecture-guide\">Software Architecture Guide — Fowler: arsitektur sebagai keputusan penting dan mahal kalau salah</a> — ringkasan halaman Software Architecture Guide</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420060847\">Arsitektur adalah penentu biaya perubahan masa depan</a> — arsitektur adalah penentu biaya perubahan masa depan</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420060928\">Arsitektur bukan kasta; dia harus hidup bersama kode</a> — arsitektur bukan kasta; dia harus hidup bersama kode</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">permanent-note (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">software-architecture (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">architecture (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">martin-fowler (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.software-architecture\">MOC: Software Architecture</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertN